md.description: The maintaining index of CFM,range from 1 to 65535.

ma.description: The maintaining alliance index of CFM,range from 1 to 65535.

remote-mep.description: The Remote Mep of CFM,range from 1 to 8191.

efm.description: Configure EFM Track instance.This track object is dependent on interface.If interface is deleted,the track object will be deleted.

efm-track.description: Configure EFM Track instance.This track object is dependent on interface.If interface is deleted,the track object will be deleted.

group-id.description: Ping-detect group ID,the upper limit of this parameter depend on the device.

tunnel-id.description: MPLS-OAM tunnel ID,the upper limit of this parameter depends on the device.

vrrp.description: Configure VRRP Track instance.This track object is dependent on interface.If interface is deleted,the track object will be deleted.

vrrp-track.description: Configure VRRP Track instance.This track object is dependent on interface.If interface is deleted,the track object will be deleted.

group-id.description: The virtual router ID of VRRP group,range from 1 to 255.

instance-id.description: SQA instance ID, the upper limit of this parameter depends on the device.

meg.description: MPLS-TP OAM meg index, the upper limit of this parameter depends on the device.

interface.description: Configure interface Track instance.This track object is dependent on interface.If interface is deleted,the track object will be deleted.

interface-track.description: Configure interface Track instance.This track object is dependent on interface.If interface is deleted,the track object will be deleted.

interface-status-type.description: The type of interface protocol status,range from 0 to 5,the full set of status values as follows:0 Layer2 status(default);1 Layer3 status;2 layer2 exclude SD status; 3 layer3 exclude SD status; 4 bidirectional SD status; 5 RX SD status.

tunnel-id.description: Tunnel ID,the upper limit of this parameter depends on the device.

prefix-name.description:
Name of a prefix list.

These characters's ASCII unicode must be between 0x21-0x3E / 0x40-0x7E.

vrf-name.description:
VPN Routing/Forwarding instance name.

These characters's ASCII unicode must be between 0x21-0x3E / 0x40-0x7E.

group-policy.description: Track-group policy,range from 0 to 10.The default value is 0,when the default value is 0,and all the members state is down in the track-group, the track-group state will be down.

up-delay.description: Track-group delay up time.ranges from 0s to 600s(default:0s).

group-members.description: The member object of group.when the track is added to the track-group as a member,the track must be existed.If the track is deleted ,the member track will be deleted from the track-group.

group-member.description: The member object of group.when the track is added to the track-group as a member,the track must be existed.If the track is deleted ,the member track will be deleted from the track-group.

sa-binds.description: The bind instance.when the bind instance is created,the track and track-group that is used to create the bind relation must be existed.If the track or track-group is deleted, the bind relation will be deleted.

sa-bind.description: The bind instance.when the bind instance is created,the track and track-group that is used to create the bind relation must be existed.If the track or track-group is deleted, the bind relation will be deleted.

last-state-change.description: The time of last state changing.
